    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/EntryRelationshipEnum#PREDICTS> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/EntryRelationshipEnum#PREDICTED_BY> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/EntryRelationshipEnum#EQUIV> ) ;
