    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapKindEnum#BIOLOGY> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapKindEnum#CURATION> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapKindEnum#ONTOLOGY> ) ;
    linkml:permissible_values <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapKindEnum#BIOLOGY>,
