    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/VariantSelectionEnum#EXACTLY_ONE> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/VariantSelectionEnum#ONE_OR_MORE> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/VariantSelectionEnum#ZERO_OR_MORE> ) ;
