    owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapStatusEnum#OPEN> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapStatusEnum#NARROWING> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapStatusEnum#CLOSING> <https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/KnowledgeGapStatusEnum#RESOLVED> ) ;
